ness's transaction volume. If you require invoicing assistance (limited to 20 invoices/month), the service fee will be higher.</p><ul> <li>Quickbooks Online licensing: offering convenience and financial control for offshore companies in BVI/Belize: <ul> <li>No demand for in-depth accounting knowledge.</li> <li>No restrictions on access time or location.</li> </ul> </li> </ul> </div> </div><div id="rlta-can-a-non-resident-own-and-register-a-company-in-the-bvi-belize" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-can-a-non-resident-own-and-register-a-company-in-the-bvi-belize" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="can-a-non-resident-own-and-register-a-company-in-the-bvi-belize" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> Can a non-resident own and register a company in the BVI/Belize?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-can-a-non-resident-own-and-register-a-company-in-the-bvi-belize" aria-labelledby="rlta-can-a-non-resident-own-and-register-a-company-in-the-bvi-belize" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><p>Non-residents can own and operate companies in the BVI/Belize. The country encourages foreign investment and does not require physical presence for company owners.</p></div></div></div><p><div id="mod-custom1265" class="mod-custom custom"><div class='jpb-page'><div id="ifrsdm" class="t4b-box glac-box-expand glac-box-collapsed"><p id="i1mya"> We offer a comprehensive range of accounting and tax services for offshore companies. Our services include: </p><div><ul id="iubi7" class="fa-ul"><li id="iro6g"><span id="ixg85" class="fa-li"><i class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"> </i></span><span id="imxvg">Monthly/Annual Tax Accounting services for offshore companies.</span></li><li id="ihd8k"><span class="fa-li"><i id="i6whf" class="fa-solid fa-angle-right"> </i></span><span id="iyx5n">QuickBooks